name: Barong and Payas Agung
description: There are two objects contained in the picture, first object (on the right) there is a woman who wears traditional Balinese cloths called "payas agung", payas agung is usually used at weddings or traditional ceremonies.  Then the second object (on the left), there is "Barong", Barong is one of the traditional Balinese arts, barong is usually used as part of balinese ceremonies.
